name: html-parser-react
description: the parser for html string transform to react dom

scripts.initial: cd example && npm i && npm start
scripts.version:s: npm version patch -m '[patch]' && cd package && npm version patch -m '[patch]'
scripts.version:m: npm version minor -m '[minor]' && cd package && npm version minor -m '[minor]'
scripts.version:b: npm version major -m '[major]' && cd package && npm version major -m '[major]'
